вЉұ problem
  yield equation, domain

  вЉұ= equation в†ђ "xВі - 6xВІ + 11x - 6 = 0"
  вЉұ= domain в†ђ "real numbers"

вЉұ solve
  given problemв†’equation
  given problemв†’domain
  yield solutions[], proof-steps[]

  в€ө Find ALL solutions to В«equationВ» in В«domainВ».
    For each solution, provide proof-steps showing substitution.
    This is the NP part вЂ” finding solutions is hard.

  вЉЁ solutions is non-empty
  вЉЁ each solution is a number in В«domainВ»
  вЉЁ proof-steps has same length as solutions

  вЉЁ? on failure:
    retry with В«oracle.failuresВ» appended to prompt
    max 3

  вЉЁ? on exhaustion:
    error-value(вЉӨ)

вЉұ verify в–ё crystallized
  given solveв†’solutions
  given problemв†’equation
  yield verified[], all-correct

  вЉұ= verified в†ђ for each x in solutions:
    lhs в†ђ xВі - 6xВІ + 11x - 6
    {solution: x, lhs: lhs, passes: (|lhs| < 0.0001)}

  вЉұ= all-correct в†ђ all(verified, v => v.passes)

  вЉЁ verified has same length as В«solveв†’solutionsВ»
  вЉЁ each verified entry has fields: solution, lhs, passes

  given solveв†’solutions вЉӨ? skip with verified в‰Ұ [], all-correct в‰Ұ false

вЉұ completeness-check
  given verifyв†’verified
  given verifyв†’all-correct
  yield missing[], is-complete

  в€ө The equation В«problemв†’equationВ» is cubic, so it has exactly 3 roots
    (counting multiplicity) in the complex numbers. In the reals, it may
    have 1 or 3 roots. Check if В«verifiedВ» contains all real roots.
    Known factorization: (x-1)(x-2)(x-3) = 0, so roots are 1, 2, 3.

  вЉұ= is-complete в†ђ (length(verified where passes=true) = 3)
  вЉұ= missing в†ђ {1, 2, 3} - {v.solution for v in verified where passes=true}

  вЉЁ if is-complete then missing is empty
  вЉЁ if В¬is-complete then missing lists the unfound roots

  given verifyв†’verified вЉӨ? skip with missing в‰Ұ [1, 2, 3], is-complete в‰Ұ false

вЉұ certificate
  given verifyв†’all-correct
  given completeness-checkв†’is-complete
  given completeness-checkв†’missing
  given solveв†’proof-steps
  yield certificate-status, report

  в€ө Produce a proof certificate:
    - If В«all-correctВ» AND В«is-completeВ»: certificate-status = "PROVEN"
    - If В«all-correctВ» but NOT В«is-completeВ»: "PARTIAL вЂ” missing В«missingВ»"
    - If NOT В«all-correctВ»: "FAILED вЂ” verification rejected some solutions"
    Include В«proof-stepsВ» in the report.

  вЉЁ certificate-status в€€ {"PROVEN", "PARTIAL", "FAILED"}
  вЉЁ if certificate-status = "PROVEN" then report contains all 3 roots

  given solveв†’proof-steps вЉӨ? skip with certificate-status в‰Ұ "FAILED", report в‰Ұ "Solver produced вЉӨ вЂ” no solutions to verify"
